Merror version 1.4
===================

ABOUT

Merror is a perl class implementing an OOP way of errorhandling with the abbility of
getting a stacktrace of an error.

DOCUMENTATION

See "perldoc Merror"

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

To install perl into another location (e.g.: you are not root)
type:
    perl Makefile.PL PREFIX=/home/foouser/perllib
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    strict
    warnings

